****Creating a group in Linux****

  Considering a company has 2 groups 
1. Admin Group
2. Developer Group

1. Admin group has full access -> They can read,write,execute.
2. Developer group has limited access based on Requirement 

Command : groupadd groupname

Note : GroupName can be anything 

To Add User to the Group we have other command :

Command : usermod -aG groupname username 
